description: Removes the association of tags from a DAX resource. You can call UntagResource up to 5 times per second, per account.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The name of the DAX resource from which the tags should be removed.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: A list of tag keys. If the DAX cluster has any tags with these keys, then the tags are removed from the cluster. (string) ---

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The tag keys that have been removed from the cluster.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: The key for the tag. Tag keys are case sensitive. Every DAX cluster can only have one tag with the same key. If you try to add an existing tag (same key), the existing tag value will be updated to the new value.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: The value of the tag. Tag values are case-sensitive and can be null.
